# ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.high

**Case**

Geo-tracking accuracy is high.

## Declaration

```swift
case high
```

## Discussion

This value indicates that visual localization is complete and geo-tracking accuracy is very good.

## Accuracies

- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.undetermined**: Geo-tracking accuracy is undetermined.
- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.low**: Geo-tracking accuracy is low.
- **ARGeoTrackingStatus.Accuracy.medium**: Geo-tracking accuracy is average.
